                    <div class="about-text">
                        <p>T.S.K.V. Spartacus' powerlifting section is dedicated to developing strong, technical lifters in a supportive community. We focus on the three main powerlifting movements: squat, bench press, and deadlift.</p>
                        <p>Our section welcomes lifters of all experience levels, from complete beginners to competitive athletes. We provide structured training programs, technical coaching, and competition opportunities throughout the academic year.</p>
                        <p>As part of the Royal Dutch Strength Sports and Fitness Federation (KNKF), our members have the opportunity to compete at regional and national powerlifting competitions.</p>
                        <div class="button-container">
