                        <li>Flat-soled shoes (for squatting and deadlifting)</li>
                        <li>Water bottle</li>
                        <li>Towel</li>
                        <li>Optionally: lifting belt, wrist wraps, knee sleeves, squat shoes</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

