        <!-- KNKF Student Status Section -->
        <section id="knkf" class="section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">SUBMITTING YOUR STUDENT STATUS TO THE KNKF</h2>
                <p>As a student powerlifter, you can register with the Royal Dutch Strength Sports and Fitness Federation (KNKF) at a discounted rate. Here's how to submit your student status:</p>
                
                <ol class="steps">
                    <li>
                        <h3>FIND YOUR ENROLLMENT CERTIFICATE</h3>
                        <p>Locate your current enrollment certificate in OSIRIS (for university students) or StudieLink (for HBO students).</p>
                        <p><strong>Osiris:</strong> Go to profile > My Details > Documents. Download your 2024/2025 enrollment certificate.</p>
                        <p><strong>StudieLink:</strong> Make a screenshot of your enrollment under 'Opleidingen'.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <h3>SEND YOUR DOCUMENTATION</h3>
                        <p>Email your enrollment certificate and the location of your education to <a href="mailto:powerlifting@tskvspartacus.nl" target="_blank"><span class="highlight">powerlifting@tskvspartacus.nl</span></a></p>
                        <p>Our competition secretary will ensure the KNKF receives the document to register your student status.</p>
                    <li> 
                        <h3>COMPLETE KNKF REGISTRATION</h3>
                        <p>4.1 Register with the KNKF through the <a href="https://knkf.banster.nl/lid_worden_lid_worden"><span class="highlight">Banster member portal</span></a></p>
                        <p>4.2 Select "Competition member" for the billing model</p>
                        <p>4.3 Select "Powerlifting" for the sport</p>
                        <p>4.4 Complete the mandatory e-learning module at the Doping Authority</p>
                        <p>4.5 Inform our competition secretary of your KNKF membership number and date of birth</p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
                
                <div class="knkf-registration">
                    <h3>IMPORTANT NOTES</h3>
                    <p>For competition registrations, it can take up to one day for your membership to synchronize with the systems.</p>
                    <p>The automatic collection by the KNKF will only take place later. Do not transfer any fees without asking first.</p>
                    <p>If you need assistance with the registration process, please contact our competition secretary at <a href="mailto:powerlifting@tskvspartacus.nl"><span class="highlight">powerlifting@tskvspartacus.nl</span></a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>




